 Creating New User/Schema/Account :- 
 ------------------------------------------------------

 => only DBAs are having permissions to create new user

  step 1 :-  connect as system

           USERNAME :-  SYSTEM/TIGER

  step 2 :-  create user

Syntax :-
--------------

     CREATE USER <name> IDENTIFIED BY <pwd>
     DEFAULT TABLESPACE USERS
     QUOTA UNLIMITED ON USERS ;

 Ex :- 

   CREATE USER BATCH54 IDENTIFIED BY ORACLE
   DEFAULT TABLESPACE USERS
   QUOTA UNLIMITED ON USERS ;

step 3 :-  granting permissions to user

   GRANT CONNECT,RESOURCE TO BATCH54 ;

                    connect  => to connect to db
                    resource => to create tables
                    dba          =>  all permissions 

Changing password :-
------------------------------

 => both user & admin can change password 

 By User :-          (BATCH54/ORACLE)
